                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Story -->
    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
                    <h2 class="section-title mb-4" style="color: @primaryColor;">The La Bella Journey</h2>
                    <div class="story-content">
                        <p class="lead mb-4">
                            Founded with a passion for elegance and a commitment to quality, La Bella Scarves emerged
                            as a celebration of femininity and sophistication. What began as a humble venture has
                            blossomed into a beloved brand, touching the lives of women across Egypt and beyond.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Our journey started with a simple belief: every woman deserves to feel beautiful, confident,
                            and special. We saw scarves not just as accessories, but as expressions of personality,
                            mood, and style. Each piece in our collection is thoughtfully designed to complement
                            your individuality while providing the ultimate comfort and luxury.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

