                                standards in every stitch and pattern.
                            </p>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3">
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-2" style="color: @primaryColor;"></i>Premium Quality Materials</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-2" style="color: @primaryColor;"></i>Ethical Production Practices</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-2" style="color: @primaryColor;"></i>Customer-Centric Approach</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-2" style="color: @primaryColor;"></i>Sustainable Packaging</li>
