                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-star mr-2" style="color: @primaryColor;"></i>Launch sustainable clothing line</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-star mr-2" style="color: @primaryColor;"></i>Establish flagship stores</li>
                                <li><i class="fas fa-star mr-2" style="color: @primaryColor;"></i>Create educational style workshops</li>
                            </ul>
